{"tid":2171960,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"90後想買樓最緊要係乜？","createTime":"2020-08-24T09:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T16:04:22.000Z","uid":365808,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65239f4949caa7b0eb3800d2e70a3bec88f8889a","tid":2171960,"uid":365808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"當然係早出世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你好上進24,25歲啱啱儲到少少錢，2016年樓價又比人炒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活係咁既政府底下，上一代人齊齊剝削下一代<br />\n有得你賺你賺唔賺先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一句講哂，90後如果買唔到樓要怪就怪自己遲出世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申利: 好彩有個早出世而又上進既老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2770020222eaec06ef9739d9e57d071b92a92261","tid":2171960,"uid":303880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"總結係最尾個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"df61569b8d8d57eec2d8fb97516baabc1cf880bd","tid":2171960,"uid":365808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2770020222eaec06ef9739d9e57d071b92a92261","tid":2171960,"uid":303880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"總結係最尾個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"有感而發，因為靠自己真係買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940f0360b5250c86431e575eb19c3a567da06e98","tid":2171960,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"00後仲慘"},{"pid":"9b2f2d8f5e010a98d14a5b4c01af8d6906aed15a","tid":2171960,"uid":365808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"眼見大部份住舊區私樓嘅人都唔係因為佢哋收入高，只係單純地早出世"},{"pid":"c381ad62b622296d02cbad0b5267f62395f94fe2","